OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 03 APR
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1938FHaving previously relied solely
OL,7,Fon British Movietone News and
OL,8,FGaumont-British News cinema newsreels,
OL,9,Fthe BBC Television Service today
OL,10,Fbroadcast its first news bulletin,
OL,11,Faccording to surviving Radio Times
OL,12,Flistings.
OL,13,
OL,14,FThe initial daily sound-only bulletin
OL,15,Fon Sunday 3rd April is listed as News
OL,16,Ffrom the National Programme, whilst
OL,17,Fsubsequent programmes are billed as
OL,18,Fsimply News Bulletin and described as
OL,19,F"A recording of the Third News from the
OL,20,FNational programme."
OL,21,
OL,22,FCinema newsreels continued to be shown
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBOn This DayCClean FeedFNat TV
